description: Looking for a quick and easy dinner the whole family will love? This zingy chicken and cheese taco recipe using soft tortillas is for you.
keywords: Chicken dishes,Quick & easy dinner,High protein,Seafood free,Tree nut free,Kale,Low sugar,Chicken,Peanut free
name: Tangy Chicken Tacos Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat oil in a large frying pan over high heat. Cook chicken, stirring occasionally, for 8 minutes or until browned and cooked through. Add taco seasoning from kit and cook, stirring, for 1 minute or until fragrant.
Meanwhile, heat tortillas from kit according to packet instructions. Make kaleslaw kit according to packet instructions.
Top tortillas with cheese, kaleslaw, chicken and salsa from kit. Serve tacos with lime wedges.
